  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to examine technical feasibility and diagnostic yield of new 20-gauge Procore
      needle for EUS-guided fine needle biopsy in solid lesions by comparing with 22-gauge Procore
      needle. The study design is prospective, randomized study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
